Einstein Discovery Capacities and Requirements

Einstein Discovery has limits for CRM Analytics datasets, models, and predictions.
CRM Analytics Dataset Requirements:
Number of rows: 400-20,000,000
Number of columns: 3-50
Model Limits:
Models created or trained per org per day: 100
Models created or trained per org per month: 500 (5000 with additional licenses)
Concurrent model creation and training processes per org: 2
Prediction Definition Limits:
Active prediction definitions: Unlimited (CRM Analytics Plus), 10 (Einstein Prediction)
Unique prediction definitions on a single entity: 3
Active models deployed to a single prediction definition: 10
Prediction Limits:
Predictions requested per org in 24 hours: 5,000,000 (500,000 without high-volume writeback)
Records that can be scored per org in 24 hours: 1,000,000
On-demand prediction requests per org in 24 hours: 50,000
On-demand prediction requests per user per hour: 2,000

Other Limitations:
Multivalue fields aren't supported in Einstein Discovery.
